nodes.text: The Semblan eel was a species of eel native to the planet Sembla, which featured enormous coral reefs in its oceans. During the Cold War between the Galactic Republic and the Sith Empire, the Semblan eel was discovered among the reefs for the first time by explorers.
The Semblan eel was first mentioned in the Bioanalysis crewskill mission "The Reefs of Sembla" in Star Wars: The Old Republic, a video game released by BioWare and LucasArts.
